      "description": "Clean, well-kept good-condition example that shows nicely and has clearly been cared for. It presents well inside and out, with a tidy overall appearance and only the normal wear you\u2019d expect for its age. A solid, honest car that\u2019s easy to like and ready for its next owner.",
